      "widgets_values": [
        "# AudioSR - Quick Setup Guide\n\n## 📁 Model Folder Structure\n\nCreate this folder in your ComfyUI installation:\n\n```\nComfyUI/\n└── models/\n    └── AudioSR/\n        ├── audiosr_basic_fp32.safetensors\n        └── audiosr_speech_fp32.safetensors\n```\n\n## 📥 Download Models\n\n| Model | Download Link | Best For |\n|-------|---------------|----------|\n| Basic | [audiosr_basic_fp32.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/AudioSR/resolve/main/AudioSR/audiosr_basic_fp32.safetensors) | Music, sound effects, general audio |\n| Speech | [audiosr_speech_fp32.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/AudioSR/resolve/main/AudioSR/audiosr_speech_fp32.safetensors) | Voice, vocals, speech |\n\n**[→ View all models on HuggingFace](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/AudioSR/tree/main/AudioSR)**\n\n## 🎚️ Simple Workflow\n\n```\nLoad Audio → AudioSR → Preview Audio / Save Audio\n```\n\n## ⚙️ Recommended Settings\n\n| Setting | Value | Description |\n|---------|-------|-------------|\n| Steps | `50` | Quality vs speed (50 = good, 100 = best) |\n| Guidance | `3.5` | How faithful to input (3-5 is good range) |\n| Model | `speech` or `basic` | Choose based on your audio type |\n\n## 💻 Requirements\n\n- **GPU:** 6GB+ VRAM (8GB+ recommended)\n- **RAM:** 12GB+ recommended\n\n## 🔗 Links\n\n- [GitHub Repository](https://github.com/Saganaki22/ComfyUI-AudioSR)\n- [Models on HuggingFace](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/AudioSR/tree/main/AudioSR)\n- [Original Paper](https://arxiv.org/abs/2309.07314)\n"
      ],
